OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry and
OL,6,Flargely clear evening and night though
OL,7,Fbreezy. Cloud will increase from the
OL,8,Fwest around dawn, with perhaps the odd
OL,9,Fspot of rain over the Pennines, but
OL,10,Fstaying dry elsewhere. Windy over high
OL,11,Fground. Feeling cooler than recently.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FDry but rather cloudy
OL,14,Finitially, with sunny spells
OL,15,Fdeveloping in the east to become more
OL,16,Festablished during the afternoon.
OL,17,FGenerally cloudy overnight, with
OL,18,Foutbreaks of mostly light rain
OL,19,Fspreading eastwards.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
