OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,6,FTurning increasingly unsettled on
OL,7,FTuesday with rain and showers.
OL,8,FWednesday starts off sunny, then
OL,9,Fclouding over with showers later.
OL,10,FSunny spells developing after a wet
OL,11,Fand windy start on Thursday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
